CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1945 reads: "Honeymoon! - The former Evelyn Howard, daughter of Mrs. Helen Bumry of Junilla Street, was recently married to David Kirkley of New York. Mr. and Mrs. Kirkley are spending their honeymoon in Huntington, W.Va. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Evelyn Howard wearing crushed velvet wrap with thin brooch closure and flowers in hair, posed in Harris Studio
